name: The stories of sky and water

metadata.name: Talai Khan
metadata.description:
The lord of the flooding water surface, lives at the mouth of 17 seas and has dominion over all the earth's waters.

I painted this artwork under the impression of the Mediterranean Sea that washes the shores of Turkey. Then I turned to the mythology of that country and immediately understood how the painting would be called.

Oil on canvas
30x60 cm
Year: 2022

Daria Prostova
NFT: 5652 × 2759 px
